     MASTER SCROLL WRAPPER  (1300vh)
     Scene 1 : 0–400vh    sticky image + panels
     Scene 2 : 400–800vh  JS-pinned video + panels
     Scene 3 : 800–1200vh JS-pinned image + switch
     Buffer  : 1200–1300vh
══════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<div id="scroll-wrapper">

